{"tid":2040050,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"香港格言？","createTime":"2020-05-28T10:35:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T13:48:09.000Z","uid":69696,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"4725bef77d443336db6f43b2ac255e2f03a5d2e8","tid":2040050,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:35:53.000Z","msg":"我地有歌、旗、口號，好似仲爭句格言<br />\n<br />\n下面列左其他國家既格言俾大家參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n法國：<br />\nLibert&eacute;, &eacute;galit&eacute;, fraternit&eacute;<br />\nLiberty, equality, fraternity<br />\n自由、平等、博爱<br />\n<br />\n希臘／烏拉圭：<br />\nLiberty or death<br />\n不自由，毋寧死<br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭：<br />\nGlory to Ukraine! Glory to the heroes!<br />\n榮耀歸於烏克蘭！榮耀歸於英雄！<br />\n<br />\nKingdom of Sarawak：<br />\nDum spiro spero<br />\nWhile I breathe, I hope<br />\n一息尚存，希望仍在。<br />\n<br />\nLiberia：<br />\nThe love of liberty brought us here<br />\n對自由的熱愛帶我們來到這裡"},{"pid":"1f2600f6bcd23525981c622d9edf689596f91301","tid":2040050,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:38:05.000Z","msg":"弱小曾經讓我們懦怯，直至我們了解到智慧的光輝。"},{"pid":"f27023863d94b90bce6034c18c58160b006007fd","tid":2040050,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1f2600f6bcd23525981c622d9edf689596f91301","tid":2040050,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:38:05.000Z","msg":"弱小曾經讓我們懦怯，直至我們了解到智慧的光輝。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:39:34.000Z","msg":"英文係咩？"},{"pid":"5b66cb0f118e8220fb93f20b71816873bfc243e5","tid":2040050,"uid":199893,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:40:33.000Z","msg":"If we burn, we burn with you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4635e66801df3a19fbbc3e5b8fc3aa56641d531d","tid":2040050,"uid":4917,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:40:36.000Z","msg":"唯利是圖，投機炒賣"},{"pid":"8bbefabca6fdb0c7729d1e223ea9883403df